data.description: WOW! Welcome home to this beautifully remodeled 4 bedroom 3 bath home in Rolling Hills Ranch! This home features one bedroom and full bath downstairs along with a total of 1936 SF of living space.  This home has been recently remodeled to include fresh paint inside and outside, new quartz kitchen counters, new vinyl plank flooring downstairs, new carpet upstairs, new gas range/oven and microwave, new hardware and so much more!  Also enjoy central heat and AC, attached 2-car garage, mountain views from the backyard and primary bedroom, 4 community pools and parks, award-winning schools and close proximity to all kinds of shopping!  HOA is low ($126/mo) and there is NO mello-roos in this community! Don't wait, this one will sell fast!
